Humble Watch

This project is a derivative/fork of Feuerlord2/Humble-RSS-Site:
https://github.com/Feuerlord2/Humble-RSS-Site

Original project author: Daniel Winter / Feuerlord2.

The upstream project is licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
This repository retains the upstream license and includes local modifications by ThresholdOps.

Local modifications include, among other changes:
- bundle end date display in RSS content,
- time-left calculation fields,
- combined all.rss output,
- all.json and urgent.json outputs,
- details.json tier and bundle item output,
- seen.json active-bundle snapshot for new-bundle detection,
- configurable interest matching through config/interests.json,
- static GitHub Pages dashboard over all.json and details.json,
- live countdown display,
- expandable tier chip UI,
- Discord digest notification workflow,
- GitHub Actions workflow changes for manual and scheduled generation.

This project is not affiliated with Humble Bundle, Inc.
